7 AS INTRODUCED
8 An Act relating to state identification; amending 47
O.S. 2021, Section 6-105.3, as last amended by
9 Section 4, Chapter 330, O.S.L. 2025 (47 O.S. Supp.
2025, Section 6-105.3), which relates to
10 identification cards for Oklahoma residents;
prohibiting identification card fees for Oklahoma
11 high school students; defining term.
